Acknowledgments

Special thanks to the IIIT Delhi Sponsorship Team for providing the content and supporting materials for this project.
This script uses Python's built-in smtplib for email handling and pandas for reading Excel files.
Example Output
For each company, you will see output like:

Processing ABC Corp (abc@company.com)
Attachment Odyssey'25-Sponsorship-proposal.pdf added.
Email sent to abc@company.com
This lets you know that the email was sent successfully with the attachment.

This README provides a clear and structured explanation for users interested in automating their sponsorship email outreach for Odyssey'25. You can share it with contributors and anyone who wants to implement this script.
